<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٦٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١١٢٠٨ - عَنِ الثَّوْرِيِّ، عَنْ خَالِدٍ الْحَذَّاءِ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنْ طَلَّقَهَا وَاحِدَةً وَهُوَ يَنْوِي ثَلَاثًا فَهِيَ وَاحِدَةٌ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>